quran[12]{c,v,t}:
  43,11,"On jippinr…óo to…ìo ka kammuu, yeru haaju, Men wuurnitiri ngo leydi maayndi. Ko non yaltinirte…óon"
  43,12,"On tagu…óo nooneeji …óin fow, O wa…óirani on e laa…óe …óen e neemoraa…ói …óin, ko wa…ó…óoron"
  43,13,"fii yo on fotondir e hoore majji, refti annditon neema Joomi mon On, tuma fotondir…óon e majji, wi'on ontuma: \"Senayee woodanii eltan…óo men …óum On, men wonaano taaqanaa…ìe …óum"
  43,14,"menen non, ko ka Joomi amen woni ko men ruttotoo"
  43,15,"∆Åe wa…óani Mo ge…ìal e jeyaa…ìe Makko …ìen ! Pellet, on ne…ó…óanke ko yeddu…óo …ìanngu…óo"
  43,16,"Kaa woo O jogiti …ìi…ó…ìe rew…ìe e ko O tagi kon, O heertinani on …ìi…ó…ìe wor…ìe …ìen"
  43,17,"Si go…ó…óo e ma…ì…ìe wewliniraama ko o wa…óirani kon Hinaranke On misal, yeeso makko ngon ni…ì…ìita metteendi hombo suu…ói"
  43,18,"E ko on ne'etee…óo e cu…óaari, hara kanko on ka yeddondiral, wanaa o …ìannginoowo haala"
  43,19,"∆Åe wa…ói Malaa'ikaa…ìe taw…ìe …ìen ko jeyaa…ìe Jom Hinaranke On, rew…ìe ! Kere …ìe seedino tageede …ìen? Awa fii seedagol ma…ì…ìe ngol winndete, …ìe lamnditoyee"
  43,20,"∆Åe wi'iti: \"Si Jom Hinaranke On haajuno, men rewataano …ìe\". ∆Åe alanaa …óum hay e ganndal; …ìe wonaali, si wanaa hi…ìe fena"
  43,21,"Kaa ko Deftere Men addani …ìe ado ndee …óoo, hara ko nden woni ko …ìe jogitii"
  43,22,"Si ko woni, …ìe wi'iu: \"Menen men tawu baabiraa…ìe amen …ìen e diina, haray ko e batteeji ma…ì…ìe men feewirta"
